import "../../styles/components/roundchart.css"
import { RadialBarChart , RadialBar , ResponsiveContainer } from "recharts"

function RoundChart ({input}) {
    let tab = [{score:(input.score)*100,fill:"red"},{score:100,fill:"transparent"}]
    console.log(tab)

    return (
        <ResponsiveContainer width="30%" height={300}>
            <RadialBarChart innerRadius="50%" outerRadius="80%" barSize={10} data={tab} startAngle={90} endAngle={450}>
                <RadialBar minAngle={15} clockWise={true} dataKey="score" background={true} />
            </RadialBarChart>
        </ResponsiveContainer>
    )
}

export default RoundChart
